public static final class Qt.TextFlag
extends java.lang.Enum
implements QtEnumerator

This enum type is used to define some modifier flags. Some of these flags only make sense in the context of printing: You can use as many modifier flags as you want, except that Qt::TextSingleLine and Qt::TextWordWrap cannot be combined.

Flags that are inappropriate for a given use are generally ignored.
